This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it discusses the use of capsule networks for image classification tasks. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new approach to improve the scalability and accuracy of capsule networks. Additionally, the paper involves the use of dynamic routing, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it discusses the generalization capability of the network.
